text.tspan: Channel 1 (Yellow) - Per. (P3.3): Write command event received on GATT server
Channel 2 (Blue) - Cen. (P5.0): Radio TX from GATT Client (connection events)
Channel 3 (Purple) - Cen. (P3.3): Start of API write call on GATT client
Channel 4 (Green) - Per. (P5.0): Radio TX (Ack.) from GATT Server
Indeterministic delay from API call to the next
The delay is approx. uniformly distributed between zero
and the period of connection events.
Appox. 350 μs from start of connection event
to start of event received on peripheral.
